# Creative Writing Assistant

This is a project aimed at helping writers generate creative content, such as story ideas, character names, and plot twists.

## Features

- Generate random story ideas
- Suggest character names
- Provide plot twists

## Installation

To install the project, clone the repository and install the dependencies.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/creative-writing-assistant.git
cd creative-writing-assistant
pip install -r requirements.txt
